Davenport.Claus Untiedt House: The Claus Untiedt House is a historic building located in the West End of Davenport, Iowa, United States. It and the neighboring Joachim Plambeck House are replicas of each other, although the Plambeck House has more alterations. The 2-story Late Victorian style residence features a three-bay façade with a side entrance and a front gable.
